{"word":"G179 - ἀκατάλυτος - akatálytos - ak-at-al'-oo-tos - Endless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀκατάλυτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">akatálytos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ak-at-al'-oo-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Endless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அழியாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"indissoluble, not subject to destruction"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2647 - καταλύω - katalýō - kat-al-oo'-o/2647\">G2647</a>; <i>indissoluble</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>permanent:</i> - endless.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G179/179\">G179</a>, <a href=\"#/G1955/1955\">G1955</a>, <a href=\"#/G1956/1956\">G1956</a>, <a href=\"#/G2646/2646\">G2646</a>, <a href=\"#/G2647/2647\">G2647</a>, <a href=\"#/G3083/3083\">G3083</a>, <a href=\"#/G3084/3084\">G3084</a>, <a href=\"#/G3085/3085\">G3085</a>, <a href=\"#/G3086/3086\">G3086</a>, <a href=\"#/G3089/3089\">G3089</a>, <a href=\"#/G359/359\">G359</a>, <a href=\"#/G360/360\">G360</a>, <a href=\"#/G487/487\">G487</a>, <a href=\"#/G629/629\">G629</a>, <a href=\"#/G630/630\">G630</a>"}]}